---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Tim Raysby">
  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-10 items-start">
    <img
      src="/headshot.png"
      alt="Tim Raysby"
      width="200"
      height="200"
      class="w-full md:w-48 h-auto border border-charcoal-lighter"
    />

    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-green mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-green"></span>
        About
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Intent-driven engineer.<br/>
        <em>AI orchestrator.</em><br/>
        Problem solver.
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-ink-dim text-sm font-mono max-w-prose">
        <p>I build agentic AI systems and ship production code where ownership meets velocity.</p>

        <p>Most of the AI economy is a tax on attention — every prompt, every memory, every artifact you produce billed by the token, owned by someone else. There is a different way: infrastructure that runs on the machine in front of you.</p>

        <p>By day I am a senior engineer at a major insurer. Evenings and weekends I build NEXUS, my personal AI infrastructure. This site, every essay, every product — produced on it.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-charcoal-lighter">
    <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-green mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-green"></span>
      Operator profile
    </p>
    <pre class="bg-charcoal-light border border-charcoal-lighter rounded-sm p-6 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed text-ink-dim"><code><span class="text-ink-dimmer"># /etc/timraysby.yaml</span>
<span class="text-green">name</span>:         Tim Raysby
<span class="text-green">role</span>:         senior engineer @ Fortune 100 insurer (day)
              builder of NEXUS (evenings &amp; weekends)
<span class="text-green">location</span>:     Greenville, SC
<span class="text-green">runtime</span>:      local-first
<span class="text-green">philosophy</span>:   my tokens, my business
<span class="text-green">shipped</span>:      NEXUS &mdash; agentic AI on my own hardware
                this site, every essay, every product

<span class="text-ink-dimmer"># constraints</span>
<span class="text-green">sabbath</span>:      Sundays &mdash; rest is structural, not residual
<span class="text-green">data</span>:         no cloud-resident personal context
<span class="text-green">scope</span>:        evenings &amp; weekends only

<span class="text-ink-dimmer"># dependencies</span>
<span class="text-green">requires</span>:     [ coffee, waterfall hikes, SUP boarding, travel, time with my wife ]
<span class="text-green">recharges-on</span>: slow weekends that earn the building

<span class="text-ink-dimmer"># interface</span>
<span class="text-green">contact</span>:      contact@timraysby.com</code></pre>
  </section>
</Layout>
